6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,969
Life up everything about you, your smile, your handshake, your talk, even your walk.

7
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:27,409
Act alive.

8
00:00:27,759 --> 00:00:29,650
Broadcast good news.

9
00:00:29,838 --> 00:00:33,969
No one ever accomplished anything positive telling bad news.

10
00:00:33,969 --> 00:00:35,409
2.

11
00:00:35,838 --> 00:00:38,530
Grow the you are important attitude.

12
00:00:38,719 --> 00:00:42,369
